    "NextStep never uploads imported model files and does not include a paid or remote model catalog. Import reads only files listed in model.json, enforces storage limits, and verifies every SHA-256 checksum. This build manages verified model artifacts; on-device text generation is not connected yet." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "NextStep never uploads imported model files and does not include a paid or remote model catalog. Import reads only files listed in model.json, enforces storage limits, and verifies every SHA-256 checksum. This build manages verified model artifacts; on-device text generation is not connected yet." } },
        "zh-Hant" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "NextStep 不會上傳匯入的模型檔案，也不提供付費或遠端模型目錄。匯入時只會讀取 model.json 所列的檔案、限制儲存空間，並驗證每個 SHA-256 校驗碼。此版本可管理已驗證的模型檔案；尚未連接裝置端文字生成功能。" } }
      }
    },
